## logMessages variable

Map of all messages that can be logged from this package. The key in the map is in the format: `category`<!-- -->.`message`<!-- -->, with `category` and `message` the properties from the log entry object passed to the [LogFunction](./vm-providers.logfunction.md)<!-- -->. The value in the map is the log message in English.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
logMessages: {
    [key: string]: string;
}
```
